VMware is a cross-platform '''v'''irtual '''m'''achine soft'''ware''' emulator produced by VMware, Inc. 

Gentoo currently provides two VMware players that are able to run VMware images. Each player has a respective article:

* [[VMware/Player|VMware player]] - A free as (in beer) player for virtual machine images.
* {{Package|app-emulation/vmware-workstation}} - A commercial desktop application that costs money.

